{
  "texts": [
    "CP: (Content Proliferation) Variable used to describe the use of GenAI in proliferating, sharing, translating, or expediting Example 1: (CC) \"Deepfakes\" \"AIgenerated speech material\" \"AIdeveloped images\" Example 2: (CP) \"Bot farms\" \"AI powered social media accounts\" \"AI tools translating speeches in real time\" the delivery of material to an audience.",
    "HT: (Hypertargeting) Variable used to describe the application of GenAI to specifically target an individual or group.",
    "UC: (Unclear) Variable referring to the unspecified use of GenAI by an actor relevant to an election.",
    "Example 3: (HT) \"AI campaign based on a demographic constituency\" Example 4: (UC) \"Use of AI by political candidate\" Actor FA: (Foreign Actor) Variable referring to the usage of GenAI by a foreign power or institution (named or unnamed), relevant to an election.",
    "PPC: (Political Party or Candidate) Variable referring to the usage of GenAI by a political candidate or their party (including a former political actor), relevant to an election."
  ]
}